        ],
        "dur": 1,
        "black": true
      },
      "bgm": "story-1",
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "這份資料放在這裡可以嗎？……嗯，聽從你的命令。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "……人類果然有趣。僅僅為了驅動兵器，就要處理這麼多文件。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "調運與儲備燃料、確保彈藥資源、糧食補給、備用品補充與廢棄處理。除了對兵器本身的整修，還要顧及一切生活必需品，實在繁瑣。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "話雖如此，整理十分有效。秘書艦的工作，會讓人有種自己才是艦隊指揮者的錯覺。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "雖然不明白的事尚有不少，但比起光是戰鬥的那段時光，擔任秘書艦以來對一切的看法都有了許多變化。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "要考慮的不是如何打倒敵人，而是“如何不輸給對手”。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "以及，除了“戰鬥”之外，還有如何“生存”下去。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "指揮官，我來提交報告書了，請你查收。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "鐵血這個月的會計帳本，謄抄和整理好了，瀕臨赤字。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "節約很重要——對驅逐艦還好，說服重巡花費了很大功夫。戰艦本來就需要更多的物資，確實比較難以控制成本",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "——被摸頭了",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "能理解表揚的意義，但我不太明白，隔著布料觸摸身體這一行為有何意義？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 2,
      "say": "也不會因此增加報酬，這樣的觸摸究竟有何好處？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "原本連“表揚”這一行為都無法理解，這次算有點進步了吧。如果這算是大家所說的“進步”的話…",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "我對這種“身體接觸”依然無法理解。然而即使生出“想瞭解”的心之波瀾，也會在戰鬥來臨之時被瞬間吞噬。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "下一次，更直接地問問吧。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
